long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Boost Your Language Learning Efficiency!

Discover unfamiliar words effortlessly while reading in a foreign language. With Quizlet QuickList, you can instantly save and compile the words you want to study—no more tedious copy-pasting! Whether you’re a student, a language enthusiast, or just browsing online, this extension is your shortcut to faster, smarter learning.
